data.description:
Welcome home! This charming two-story home boasts on a spacious floor plan with hardwood floors throughout. As you enter, you are greeted by a cozy family room with plenty of natural light, a fireplace and high ceilings. The kitchen has ample counter space, cabinet space, and the dining area is conveniently located next to the kitchen.
The primary bedroom is spacious and features a large walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with a dual sink vanity. The two additional bedrooms are located upstairs and share a full bathroom. The garage is currently being used as a 4th bedroom but can be used as a media room or be converted back to garage.
Located in a great established neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from 820, shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours!
